ATTR_LEVEL

public static final java.lang.String ATTR_LEVEL
The sharing level of a newly added or moved file. This, instead of radius, is the one that a repository cares. The repository can calcuate this from a radius, but letting the pie do the calculation can localize knowledge about radius.
